column1: Description: This spreadsheet contains the IMBIE-2019 dataset for Greenland, which includes data on the annual rate of change and cumulative change in Greenland’s ice sheet mass, its surface mass balance and ice discharge anomalies, and their estimated uncertainty. The data are expressed in units of equivalent mean global sea level rise (millimetres per year – columns B, C, F, G, J and K, and millimetres – columns D, E, H, I, L and M).
Publication: Mass balance of the Antarctic ice sheet from 1992 to 2017. Nature, (2019)
